 1980|1980]]'''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|44.8% ''251,333''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''48.0%''' ''269,147''\n| style=\"background:honeyDew;\"|7.2% ''40,443''\n|-\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1976|1976]]'''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|39.0% ''244,396''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''60.5%''' ''379,907''\n| style=\"background:honeyDew;\"|0.5% ''3,200''\n|-\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1972|1972]]'''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|'''56.3%''' ''426,015''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|43.4% ''328,316''\n| style=\"background:honeyDew;\"|0.2% ''1,756''\n|-\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1968|1968]]'''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|40.0% ''306,620''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''53.6%''' ''410,546''\n| style=\"background:honeyDew;\"|6.4% ''48,746''\n|-\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1964|1964]]'''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|33.6% ''274,351''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''66.3%''' ''541,418''\n| style=\"background:honeyDew;\"|0.1% ''1,059''\n|-\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1960|1960]]'''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|45.1% ''367,688''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''54.7%''' ''446,348''\n| style=\"background:honeyDew;\"|0.2% ''1,863''\n|-\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1956|1956]]'''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|'''59.4%''' ''466,057''\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Democratic}}|40.6% ''318,723''\n| style=\"background:honeyDew;\"|0.0% ''0''\n|-\n| style=\"{{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1952|1952]]''