5)\n| -\n|-\n|Reduce to \nMedium Speed\n|Proceed at normal speed, but reduce to medium speed before the next signal\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n|[[File:Melbourne_RMS_Signal_Searchlight.png|frameless|80x80px]](40)\n|[[File:Adelaide_Flashing_Yellow.gif|frameless|95x95px]](35)\n|[[File:SA_RTMS.png|frameless|87x87px]](35)\n| -\n|-\n|Clear Medium Speed\n|Proceed at medium speed\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n|[[File:Melbourne_Medium_Clear_Signal_Searchlight.png|frameless|88x88px]](40)\n| -\n|[[File:Red_on_Green_SA.png|frameless|84x84px]](35)\n| -\n|-\n| colspan=\"10\" |'''Shunt Aspects'''\n|-\n|Shunt\n|Continue Through \nSignal on Sight\n|[[File:Shunt_Signal_Sydney.png|frameless|79x79px]]\n|[[File:SCSS_NSW_Shunt.png|frameless|87x87px]]\n|[[File:Brisbane_Real_Shunt_Signal.png|frameless|77x77px]]\n|[[File:Victorian_Two_aspect_Shunt_signal.png|frameless|85x85px]]\n|[[File:Melbourne_Shunt.png|frameless|92x92px]]\n|[[File:Adelaide_Suburban_Shunt_Signal.png|frameless|77x77px]]\n|[[File:Shunt_SA.png|frameless|86x86px]]\n|[[File:Perth_Shunt.png|frameless|81x81px]]\n|-\n|Close Up\n(Call On)\n|Continue on sight \nto train ahead\n|[[File:Sydney_Trains_Close_Up.png|frameless|87x87px]]\n|[[File:SCSS_Low_Speed.png|frameless|84x84px]]\n|[[File:Call_On_Brisbane.png|frameless|72x72px]]\n|^\n|^\n|^\n|^\n|^\n|-\n| colspan=\"10\" |'''Turnout Aspects / Add-on Indicators'''\n|-\n|Turnout Left\nClear\n|Train must slow for \nturnout to the left\n\nafter signal\n| rowspan=\"2\" | -\n| -\n|[[File:Diverge Left.png|frameless|90x90px]]\u2020\n|[[File:Two Aspect Diverge Left.png|frameless|74x74px]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[File:Melbourne_Medium_Clear_Signal_Searchlight.png|frameless|88x88px]] \u2020 \n|[[File:Diverge Left.png|frameless|90x90px]]\u2020\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[File:Red_on_Green_SA.png|frameless|84x84px]]\u2020\n|[[File:Diverge Left.png|frameless|90x90px]]\u2020\n|-\n|Turnout Right\nClear\n|Train must slow for \nturnout to the right\n\nafter signal\n| -\n|[[File:Diverge Right.png|frameless|109x109px]]\u2020\n|[[